		<td><b>bullets movement patterns</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi all,
<br />
<br />How could I program the movement of bullets with 
<br />arbitrary pattern? 
<br />
<br />say, they move straight with different angles and velocities
<br />
<br />possible for them to move in curves? 
<br />
<br />what's the easiest to handle them? as i have to monitor their
<br />movements and collisions with other objects...
<br />
<br />Blanc

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
